  (text "JMISC / JMEDIA MOUNTING NOTES:\n\nSAMTEC FTSH-130-01-L-DV-A:\n  2x30 contacts, 1.27mm pitch, SMD mezzanine\n  Mates with UNO Q board underside connectors\n  ENIG surface finish required for reliable 1.27mm pitch soldering\n  Stencil: 0.12mm aperture reduction per pad\n  Placement accuracy: ±0.05mm (use vision system in pick-and-place)\n\nMPU GPIO (1.8V):\n  QRB2210 GPIO outputs from JMISC are 1.8V\n  Route directly to TXS0108E level shifters (see level_shift sheet)\n  DO NOT connect to any 3.3V or 5V logic directly\n  1V8_REF from JMISC used as VCCA on TXS0108E\n\nMIPI ROUTING FROM B2:\n  DSI: 4-lane → CBTL04GP054 switch → LT8618SX or J_DSI FPC\n  CSI0: 2-lane shown (D0 only; expand to 4-lane if camera requires)\n  CSI1: 2-lane shown (D0 only)\n  All MIPI pairs: 100Ω differential, IPC-2221B inner layer routing\n  GND pins interleaved with signal pins — route GND vias directly to L2"
    (at 20 130 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27)) (justify left top)))
